      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified+1\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.7/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/ac91b598-57e4-11e5-86fa-5254006e85c2).  Ran 13 tests.  No failures.",
